title: #147 - Belle Delphine Arrested By British Authorities & Fousey vs Slim
description: On this episode of The H3 Podcast we look into what happened to gamer bathwater girl Belle Delphine, take a look at Fousey's boxing match, the TANK scooter, three beat slide DMCAing us, wearable chairs, Terryology, and a whole lot more!
